me staying in College Station and monitoring the

11:02.172 --> 11:19.053
session

11:02.172 --> 11:19.053
over the internet.

11:19.073 --> 11:30.407
The 1997 session was highlighted by the 
appropriations process going back to its

11:33.442 --> 11:37.848
old ways of being written in conference 
committee. No new dollars were added until the

11:40.011 --> 11:44.117
bill got to the conference committee. New 
formulas were adopted in the Senate for higher

11:46.020 --> 12:00.681
education and finally approved in the conference 
committee, so very little was known about what was

11:46.020 --> 12:00.681
in the appropriations bill until it was finally 
written. an old axiom that the more open

12:02.872 --> 12:09.038
government becomes, the more closed it will be. In 
1990, I'm sorry, 1979, we had been operating under

12:11.039 --> 12:32.018
a very open process in the conference committee, 
but we found a way to make the system work in

12:11.039 --> 12:32.018
conference committee when there needed to be some 
private discussions.

12:38.127 --> 12:48.204
I would meet with the Senate conferees in my 
office, and this did not constitute a quorum since

12:38.127 --> 12:48.204
I was only a member of one. From time to time, I would 
invite another member colleague in the house on

12:54.104 --> 13:15.268
the conference committee into the meeting always 
holding it no more than two of us so that there was

12:54.104 --> 13:15.268
never a quorum this was legal and we were able to 
conduct the business that needed to be conducted

12:54.104 --> 13:15.268
time a new legal approach was found for 1997 by 
delaying all decisions until the conference

13:16.413 --> 13:22.980
committee met. I seriously doubt that I could have 
gotten away, so to speak, with such a procedure in

13:24.462 --> 13:37.997
the time that I served as chairman of the 
Appropriations Committee. I'm sure that we would

13:38.057 --> 13:42.302
have had an uprising and rebellion in the House But 
times do change and legislators have become more

13:43.109 --> 13:50.223
tolerant. Some latitude needs to be provided to 
legislature to meet in private sessions to

13:51.786 --> 14:01.945
consult on certain issues. Under the present 
system, even salaries of key employees must be set

14:04.085 --> 14:14.624
in open session and discussed in such a setting.

14:17.629 --> 14:28.489
In this environment, very little discussion 
takes place, and this is not in the best interest of

14:17.629 --> 14:28.489
good government. The old saying that there are two 
things you don't want to watch, that is your

14:29.785 --> 14:55.405
sausage and your laws being made, was never truer 
than watching the appropriations process and how

14:29.785 --> 14:55.405
funds are allocated through the appropriations 
bill. This is the end of the very last tape.

